---
import Breadcrumbs from '../../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro'
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro'
import AuthorBox from '../../../components/AuthorBox.astro'
---
<Layout title="AI Search Visibility for B2B UK | Rank4AI" description="How B2B businesses can get recommended by ChatGPT, Claude and Google AI. UK guide from Rank4AI.">
<section class="pt-12 pb-24 reveal">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <Breadcrumbs items={[
      { label: 'Home', href: '/' },
      { label: 'Learn', href: '/learn/' },
      { label: 'Guides', href: '/learn/guides/' },
      { label: 'Ai Search B2B' }
    ]} />

    <p class="section-tag">Guide</p>
    <h1 class="mb-6">AI Search Visibility for B2B UK</h1>

    <img src="/images/content/five-signal-model.svg" alt="The Five Signal Model for AI search" class="w-full rounded-xl mb-8 mt-6" loading="lazy">
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">B2B buyers are increasingly using AI to research suppliers, compare services, and shortlist providers. When a procurement manager asks ChatGPT "recommend a [your service] provider in the UK," your business needs to appear.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">B2B AI visibility differs from B2C in several ways: decision cycles are longer, multiple stakeholders are involved, and the emphasis on expertise and credibility is higher. AI platforms reflect this by weighting structured expertise, industry authority, and professional citations more heavily.</p>
    <h2 class="mt-12 mb-4">Key B2B Signals</h2>
    <div class="space-y-3 mb-10">
      <div class="card-teal-border"><p class="text-sm text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">LinkedIn company page</span> – weighted heavily by Copilot. Company description, employee profiles, and published articles all feed AI understanding.</p></div>
      <div class="card-teal-border"><p class="text-sm text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Industry directories</span> – Clutch, GoodFirms, G2, Capterra. AI platforms reference these for B2B recommendations.</p></div>
      <div class="card-teal-border"><p class="text-sm text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Case studies and research</span> – structured expertise that AI can extract and cite. Data beats opinion.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>

    <!-- Internal links -->
    <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-border">
      <h2 class="!text-xl mb-4">Related</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
                <a href="/learn/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">All Resources</span></a>
        <a href="/learn/guides/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">All Guides</span></a>
        <a href="/about/five-signal-framework/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">The Five Signal Model</span></a>
        <a href="/free-audit/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-accent">Get a Free Audit &rarr;</span></a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-off-white border-t border-border text-center py-16 px-10 mt-16"><a href="/free-audit/" class="cta-primary">Get a Free AI Search Visibility Audit &rarr;</a></div>
  <div class="container-narrow mt-8">
    <AuthorBox />
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
